{"text":"@function _value($first-pair, $second-pair, $center: never)\n\t@if list.length($first-pair) < 2\n\t\t@return 1\n\n\t@if list.length($second-pair) < 2\n\t\t@return -1\n\n\t@return string.string(list.nth($first-pair, 2), list.nth($second-pair, 2), $center)","source":"v3-sass-sass-fairy-0044","language":"sass","framework":"general","project":"keyloop-corpus","level":"block","difficulty":"medium","score":7}
